Get ready for this Huge Show coming up! Lifted Florida Truck Show and Florida State Car Audio Finals! @lifted_florida_truck_show

Live performances by @noahhuntonmusic & @kendalltuckermusic 
Food Trucks! Vendors! Raffles! Cash prizes for best of’s! 

When: Sept 24th & 25th 
Where: Florida Strawberry Festival Grounds, Plant City, Fl 

Registration is open at www.liftedfloridatruckshow.com/register - some VIP and premium spots still available.
